One More Light is the seventh studio album by American rock band Linkin Park .
It was released on May 19 , 2017 through Warner Bros. .
Records and Machine Shop , following the 2014 album The Hunting Party .
The album 's first single , `` Heavy '' was released on March 16 , 2017 .
It is their first album with a title track .
In deciding on the title track , they felt that the song `` One More Light '' was the heart of the album .
The album features guest vocal appearances from Pusha T , Stormzy , and Kiiara , and production and songwriting collaborations with Julia Michaels , Justin Tranter , Ross Golan , Andrew Goldstein , blackbear , and Eg White .
Acoustic performances of the lead single by Chester Bennington and Mike Shinoda helped promote One More Light .
A few of them included performances with Kiiara , Waxx , and Sofia Karlberg .